This is basicly the first map I put together for CSS.
GG_Resol_Gz1 Map Info

  • Size: Small
  • Bots: Nav file included.
  • Spawn Points: 12 for each side (this map is to small for that many,  but then again I dont like lots of people on smaller maps)
  • Discription: A central room with 3 levels and two entry points for each team.
  • Creators Thoughts: Would work best with a small group of say 3v3 4v4 or so, any more then that and I personally would not like it.
  • Bugs: Only one I found when playing with bots and that was the two entry points for each team are visable for each team as they enter the central room so the bots tended to kill me before I even was able to enter the room.

I have a nother version of this map only the map and every thing in it has been stretch to be larger
